phrases: Eina-san told me I needed to make sure I had it
before I adventured in the middle floors.

Mikoto, you have leveled, but do not tense up.

Well, worrying will not help anything.
All we can do is wait and believe in them.
There is a lot of them lately.
I think it is just a coincidence, but...
You will be okay, right, Bell-kun?
Well, I think that is pretty good for our first battle in the middle floors.
They are not more than we can handle.

If we got surrounded here, it would be

because he got lucky with his magic,

I cannot wait to meet him.

We do not even have time to breathe!
Or even time to talk, too!

We will run through them, Mikoto.
I value your lives more than those of strangers
who I have never met before.
If you do not like it, you can bitch me out later!
The monsters chasing them will attack us instead!

Because it is the middle floors, I guess.
the dungeon is a cunning thing.
Each incident that happens there may be small in and of itself,
but as they add up, they become a death of a thousand cuts.
Tripping you when you can barely stand
is easier than falling off a log.
When its prey is gasping for breath,
That is when the dungeon bares its fangs.
Bell-kun's party has not come back?
And they have not been here either, have they?
If nothing else, I have not seen them.

The quest is to find Bell-kun's party!

but we fell down two floors instead.
It is a miracle all three of us survived that fall.
If it were not for my salamander wool,
that hellhound's breath would have wiped us all out.
We owe your advisor, big time.
Either way, with this leg, I am only going to slow you down.
We do not have a choice.
If we want to survive, we can also try going down to the 18th floor.
The enemies will just get stronger!
The 18th floor is one of several safe zones in the dungeon.
That is, monsters do not appear on that floor.
If we can get some higher-level adventurers
to take us back up with them,

We can probably go down a lot more quickly than we can go up.
That thing's on the 17th floor, right?
the Loki Familia should have beaten it on their way down.
Given the time it takes to respawn,
if we go now, we will get through first.
I will leave the decision to Bell-sama, our party leader.
No matter what happens, we will not blame you.

If Bell-kun does not come back...
I will blame you until the day I die.

most of our high-level members are out on the Loki Familia's expedition.
The only ones I can send down to the middle floors are Ouka and Mikoto,
and Chigusa to act as a supporter.
The others, unfortunately, would just slow you down.
Oh, I heard one of my dear friends was in trouble, so I hurried over.
With your quest to find Bell Cranel and his friends.

But it is true that I want to help Hestia.
I want to save Bell-kun, too.
Finding Bell-kun's party is my top priority now.
I want as many people as I can get.
I am counting on you, Hermes.
We will set out once the preparations are made.
Ouka, you guys get ready, too.

It will be fine as long as nobody finds out.

I hope you can babysit me.

when you find Welf, there is something I want you to give him...
Along with this message from me.

I do not think I can guarantee it.
I guess I will take one more along.

I am sorry, but I am closer to it than you are!

As long as this awful smell is around us,

I never thought I would use it this way, though.

I am good for a little more.
What are you thinking, I wonder?
I am the only one who is allowed to play with him.
